  primaryClass  = {cs.LG},
  annote        = {Closest prior result. Outcome-based RL improves faithfulness then plateaus; reward-hacked hint usage is not verbalized. We must position against this directly: our contribution is a controlled decay curve vs RL steps against a known ground-truth cue with provably CoT-blind reward.}
}

